com.googlecode.kevinarpe.papaya.container
Interface Tuple<TValue>

Type Parameters:
TValue - tuple element type; may be Object for tuples with mixed element types
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTuple
public interface Tuple<TValue>

N-element tuple, which may be empty. This interface (and abstract helper class) was created satisfy the need to easily create multi-element keys and values for maps.

Ref: http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/wiki/IdeaGraveyard

Author:
Kevin Connor ARPE (kevinarpe@gmail.com)
